<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <h2>Manages your complaints Efficiently</h2>

    <h3>General Guidelines</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Do not submit fake or inappropriate complaints.</li>
        <li>Follow system policies.</li>
        <li>Respect response time.</li>
        <li>Contact admin only if urgent.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="left-section">
            <h3>Before Submitting Complaint</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide correct personal details.</li>
                <li>Select appropriate complaint category.</li>
                <li>Write clear and detailed description.</li>
                <li>Avoid submitting duplicate complaints.</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/complaint/new">
                <button>Register your complaint here</button>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="right-section">
            <h3>After Submitting complaint make sure that</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Note your Complaint ID carefully.</li>
                <li>Use Complaint ID to track status.</li>
                <li>Wait for admin to assign staff.</li>
                <li>You will be notified once resolved.</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/track">
                <button>Track your registered complaint</button>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
